#: gtkscoremap.c:2713
msgid "Move ScoreMap Info"
msgstr "ムーブScoreMap情報"

#: gtkscoremap.c:2732
msgid ""
" - Cr = Crawford, J = Jacoby, DMP = Double Match Point, GG = Gammon Go, GS = "
"Gammon Save        \n"
"\n"
"- At each score, the corresponding grid square indicates the best "
"move        \n"
"\n"
"- Different colors correspond to different best moves (red for the most "
"frequent one, blue for the 2nd most, etc.)        \n"
"\n"
"- A darker color intensity reflects a larger equity difference with the 2nd "
"best move        \n"
"\n"
"- As usual, if at 2-ply no move equity is close to that of the best move, "
"the 3-ply or 4-ply analysis can stop at 2-ply        \n"
"\n"
"- Feel free to hover with the mouse on the different elements for more "
"details        \n"
"\n"
"- Default ScoreMap settings can be selected in the Settings > Analysis menu"
msgstr ""
" - Cr = クロフォード, J = ジャコビー, DMP = Double Match Point,GG = Gammon "
"Go, GS = Gammon Save        \n"
"\n"
"- それぞれのスコアにおいて、対応するマスが最善手を示します        \n"
"\n"
"- 異なる色は異なる最善手に対応します(赤は最も出現するムーブ、青は2番目"
"等)        \n"
"- 色の濃さは次善手とのエクイティ差が大きいことを反映します\n"
"\n"
"- 通常、2-plyの時点で最善に近いエクイティが無い場合は、3-plyまたは4-ply解析は"
"2-plyで止めることができます        \n"
"\n"
"- 各要素の上にマウスカーソルを置くと、詳細が表示されます\n"
"\n"
"- 既定のScoreMap設定は設定 > 解析 メニューから選択できます"

#: gtkscoremap.c:2750
msgid "Cube ScoreMap Info"
msgstr "キューブScoreMap情報"

#: gtkscoremap.c:2760
msgid ""
"- D = Double, ND = No Double, D/T = Double/Take, D/P = Double/Pass, TG = Too "
"Good        \n"
"\n"
"     To Double, J = Jacoby        \n"
"\n"
"- At each score, the corresponding grid square indicates the best cube "
"decision        \n"
"\n"
"- Different colors correspond to different cube decisions, as indicated by "
"the gauge        \n"
"\n"
"- A darker color intensity reflects a larger equity difference with the 2nd "
"best decision        \n"
"\n"
"- Feel free to hover with the mouse on the different elements for more "
"details        \n"
"\n"
"- Default ScoreMap settings can be selected in the Settings > Analysis menu"
msgstr ""
"- D = ダブル, ND = ノーダブル, D/T = ダブル/テイク, D/P = ダブル/パス, TG = "
"ツーグッド        \n"
"\n"
"     J = ジャコビー\n"
"\n"
"- それぞれのスコアにおいて、対応するマスが最善キューブ判断を示しま"
"す        \n"
"\n"
"- 異なる色は異なる最善キューブ判断に対応し、ゲージに表示されます        \n"
"\n"
"- 色の濃さは次善キューブ判断とのエクイティ差が大きいことを反映しま"
"す        \n"
"\n"
"- 各要素の上にマウスカーソルを置くと、詳細が表示されます        \n"
"\n"
"- 既定のScoreMap設定は 設定 > 解析 メニュー から選択できます"

